`0Help for the Combined Configuration Menu ------------------

<C> Change x -> y     - Toggle from ASCII mail downloading to QWK mail
                        downloading or vice-versa.
<A> Set Archiver Type - This leads to a sub menu which permits you to 
                        set a default archiver for archiving your mail.
<I> Set Includes      - Toggle which files are included with the QWK
                        mail packet.
<S> Show Settings     - Show your current configuration settings.
<X> Exit              - Exit to the previous menu.

Press ENTER to continue....`4
